    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited to share this one with you. This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014it basically looks and smells like it just left the dealership! It\u2019s been totally pampered its whole life, and I\u2019m only letting it go to see it go to a home where it\u2019ll be truly appreciated. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or hiccup here. Come take a look and see for yourself, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
